description: The one & only mobile bakery in Minnesota.  Serving a variety of freshly baked gourmet cupcakes, cupcake crumble sundaes, cold pressed coffee, iced lattes, and other beverages.A sheer love of baking and a life time of experience in the kitchen, gave birth to A Cupcake Social.Their love of baking and encouragement from their families made them realize they could combine their experience in the kitchen with their gift of creativity. Their desire to craft unique flavors and visual presentation will provide your guests with a memorable experience.  So whether it is uniquely created gourmet cupcakes for a small social gathering or a large wedding, you can be certain that Jess and Suzette will make your social event truly extraodinary.
name: A Cupcake Social
